profile:
Ray Blinds Inc. is a Lower Mainland based company offering Premium Blinds and Shades. Our blinds and shades include energy-efficient, motorized and cordless options, in addition to, luxurious and traditional ones to suit your sense of aesthetic. 

More than 500 fabrics to choose from.

We provide-
Zebra Blinds
Roller Blinds
Solar Blinds
Faux wood Blinds
Metal Blinds
Honeycomb Blinds
Vertical Blinds

Mechanism-
Corded Continuous loop
Cordless
Motorized
